LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorAA.label: Wood Generator 1.5kW
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorAA.description: HP : 450 Power : 1500W A very rustic generator, using water steam as source of power.
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorBA.label: Chemfuel Generator 3kW
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorBA.description: HP : 450 Power : 3000W Efficiency : 103% A rustic and simple Chemfuel generator using a reliable combustion engine coupled with an alternator to generate electricity.
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorBB.label: Chemfuel Generator 18KW
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorBB.description: HP : 450 Power : 18000W Efficiency : 118% A very large Chemfuel generator. This rustic version of the standard UN-FGEN18K is mainly used for its low cost and large capacity tank.
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorBC.label: UN-FGEN18K 18KW
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorBC.description: HP : 2400 Power : 18000W Efficiency : 118% The standard industrial Chemfuel generator UN-FGEN18K. Double injection system, double filtration system, high production rate and capacity.
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorCA.label: Industrial Generator 3KW
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorCA.description: HP : 900 Power : 3000W Efficiency : 103% An industrial armored Chemfuel generator, designed to withstand extreme conditions.
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorCB.label: Industrial Generator 6KW
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorCB.description: HP : 1800 Power : 6000W Efficiency : 106% An industrial Armored Chemfuel generator, very reliable with its reinforced structure.
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorMA.label: Armored FGEN03K 3kW
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorMA.description: HP : 3000 Power : 3000W Efficiency : 103% An armored Generator from UNSC standard. Foolproof design, high production rate, intended for military use, mainly for long-term entrenchments.
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorMB.label: Armored FGEN06K 6kW
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorMB.description: HP : 6000 Power : 6000W Efficiency : 106% An armored Generator from UNSC standard. All elements are fully shielded.
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorPA.label: Portable Generator 0.5kW
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorPA.description: HP : 150 Power : 500W Mass : 50kg A Chemfuel portable generator. Low capacity tank and low power but sufficient for most nomadic situations.
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorPB.label: Portable CGEN01K 1kW
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorPB.description: HP : 1500 Power : 1000W Mass : 100kg A military Chemfuel generator from UNSC standard. Mainly used in defence positions and outpost structures.
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorPC.label: Portable Fuel Cell 3kW
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorPC.description: HP : 450 Power : 3000W Efficiency : 175% Mass : 30kg An advanced portable Fuel Cell. Gives the fuel a very long service life. High Pressure Hydrogen divides by 4 the need for organic materials.
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorYA.label: Large Fuel Cell 12kW
LanguageData.SadjuukGeneratorYA.description: HP : 1800 Power : 12000W Efficiency : 175% An advanced Fuel Cell that converts the chemical energy of hydrogen into electricity. High Pressure Hydrogen divides by 4 the need for organic materials.
LanguageData.SadjuukPowerConduitA.label: Power Conduit
LanguageData.SadjuukPowerConduitA.description: Standard bundle of electrical cables for moving power around. Can be placed under walls and other buildings.
